1)  related:facebook.com       ====>>>>    shows websites same as facebook ==>>    example : linkedin , pinterest

2)  mumbai -rain               ====>>>>    shows information about mumbai that does not conatains rain information

3)  "how good monsoon"         =====>>>>   displays the pages which contains 'how good monsoon' 

4) Combine searches  (OR)         ==>>>>   engineering OR meedical

5) Search for a specific site     ====>>    site:.gov

